<hymn_number>1254</hymn_number>
<title>wǒ men yào chēng xiè yé hé huá 迦南1254</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men yào chēng xiè yé hé huá qiú gào tā de míng
 bǎ tā qí miào de zuò wèi chuán yáng zài wàn mín zhōng
 tā shǐ wú shù kē bīng lěng de xīn sū xǐng tā shǐ wú shù xiā yǎn zhě zhòng jiàn guāng míng
 tā shǐ làng zi zhòng huí gù lǐ gū ér zhǎo dào fù qīn yǔ xiōng dì
 zěn bù gǎn ēn nǎ zěn bù lái chēng sòng
 jué wàng de rén yīn zhǔ yǒu xī wàng zhòng xīn huò dé xīn shēng mìng
 wǒ men yào gāo jǔ zhǔ de míng wǒ men yào chuán yáng tā de míng
 jīn shēng jīn shì fèng xiàn zì jǐ gē shēng yǒng bù tíng</lyrics>
</song>